'''肿瘤坏死因子-α'''（{{lang-en|'''TNF-α'''}}）是一种涉及到系统性[[炎症|炎症]]的[[细胞因子|细胞因子]]，同时也是属于引起{{link-en|急相蛋白|Acute-phase protein|急相反应}}的众多细胞因子中的一员。主要由[[巨噬细胞|巨噬细胞]]分泌，不过有一些其它类型的细胞也能生产。 

==功能==

總括而言，腫瘤壞死因子-α 能抑制不同種流感病毒的複製，擁有強大的抗病毒效果<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Tumor Necrosis Factor Alpha Exerts Powerful Anti-Influenza Virus Effects in Lung Epithelial Cells|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1128/jvi.76.3.1071-1076.2002|last=Seo|first=S. H.|last2=Webster|first2=R. G.|date=2002-02-01|journal=Journal of Virology|issue=3|doi=10.1128/jvi.76.3.1071-1076.2002|volume=76|pages=1071–1076|issn=0022-538X}}</ref>。肿瘤坏死因子α的主要作用是调节[[免疫细胞|免疫细胞]]的功能。作为一种内源性致热原，它能够促使[[发热|发热]]，引起[[细胞凋亡|细胞凋亡]]，（通过诱使产生[[白细胞介素1族|''IL1'']]和{{link-en|白血球介素6|Interleukin 6|''IL6''}}）引发[[败血症|败血症]]，引起[[恶病体质|恶病体质]]，引发[[炎症|炎症]]，阻止[[肿瘤|肿瘤发生]]和{{link-en|病毒复制|Viral replication}}。 

肿瘤坏死因子α生产的失调被认为与许多人类疾病有关，包括[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]<ref name="pmid20692646">{{cite journal | author = Swardfager W, Lanctôt K, Rothenburg L, Wong A, Cappell J, Herrmann N | title = A meta-analysis of cytokines in Alzheimer's disease | journal = Biol Psychiatry | volume = 68 | issue = 10 | pages = 930–941 | year = 2010 | pmid = 20692646 | doi=10.1016/j.biopsych.2010.06.012}}</ref>、[[癌症|癌症]]<ref name="pmid11239407">{{cite journal | author = Locksley RM, Killeen N, Lenardo MJ | title = The TNF and TNF receptor superfamilies: integrating mammalian biology | journal = Cell | volume = 104 | issue = 4 | pages = 487–501 | year = 2001 | pmid = 11239407 | doi = 10.1016/S0092-8674(01)00237-9 }}</ref>、[[重性抑郁障碍|重性抑郁障碍]]<ref name="pmid20015486">{{cite journal | author = Dowlati Y, Herrmann N, Swardfager W, Liu H, Sham L, Reim EK, Lanctôt KL | title = A meta-analysis of cytokines in major depression | journal = Biol Psychiatry | volume = 67 | issue = 5 | pages = 446–457 | year = 2010 | pmid = 20015486 | doi=10.1016/j.biopsych.2009.09.033}}</ref>和[[肠炎|肠炎]]。<ref name="pmid12077089">{{cite journal | author = Brynskov J, Foegh P, Pedersen G, Ellervik C, Kirkegaard T, Bingham A, Saermark T | title = Tumour necrosis factor alpha converting enzyme (TACE) activity in the colonic mucosa of patients with inflammatory bowel disease | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_gut_2002-07_51_1/page/37 | journal = Gut | volume = 51 | issue = 1 | pages = 37–43 | year = 2002 | pmid = 12077089 | pmc=1773288 | doi=10.1136/gut.51.1.37}}</ref>虽然仍有争议，不过当前的研究认为肿瘤坏死因子α的水平与抑郁和肠炎有关。<ref name="pmid17206706">{{cite journal | author = Mikocka-Walus AA, Turnbull DA, Moulding NT, Wilson IG, Andrews JM, Holtmann GJ | title = Controversies surrounding the comorbidity of depression and anxiety in inflammatory bowel disease patients: a literature review | journal = Inflammatory Bowel Diseases | volume = 13 | issue = 2 | pages = 225–234 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17206706 | doi=10.1002/ibd.20062}}</ref>基因工程生产的肿瘤坏死因子α被用作{{link-en|免疫兴奋剂|Immunostimulant}}（[[国际非专利药品名称|国际非专利药品名称]]为[[他索纳明|他索纳明]]）。 肿瘤的恶变过程中，肿瘤坏死因子α常异位表达，而其过量表达同[[副甲狀腺素|副甲狀腺素]]一道与引发继发性[[高钙血症|高钙血症]]和癌症有关。

炎症過程中釋放的TNF-α與H2O2誘導的BCa轉化有關，伴血吸蟲感染的BCa患者血清中TNF-α水平顯著升高。另外，T3及T4期患者TNF-α水平高於T1及T2早期患者，提示TNF-α水平可能有助於BCa的進展<ref>葉衛豐,賀敏,吳志斌.膀胱癌患者外周血中IL-2、IFN-γ、TNF-α的表達及臨床意義.臨床和實驗醫學雜誌,2016,15(11):1064</ref>。由於TNF-α有助於BCa的形成和發展，故而可以作為評估BCa侵襲性和惡性程度的指標<ref>孫祖剛、劉碩等.炎症細胞和促炎性細胞因子在膀胱腫瘤炎症微環境中的作用概述.湖北科技學院學報(醫學版).2018年，第5期：P451-454</ref>。

